# Source PDFs. raw/*.pdf are excluded — the OCR'd PDFs themselves are large
# (~1.9 GB total, several individual files >100 MB) and reproducible from the
# war.gov manifest documented in SOURCES.md (download originals via
# `dow_uap_downloader`, then OCR via `scripts/ocr.sh`).
#
# What IS committed: raw/ocr/*.txt — plain-text extracts of every OCR'd page,
# ~10 MB total, fully grep-able, the canonical searchable form of the corpus.
raw/*
!raw/ocr/
!raw/ocr/*.txt

# .NET build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Editor / IDE
.vs/
.idea/
*.swp
